headline: KBW Raises Target on Brown & Brown, But Kept Bearish Stance
summary: Keefe, Bruyette & Woods bumped its price target on Brown & Brown (NYSE:BRO) from $100 to $102 on June 13, but kept its Underperform rating in place. The change came on the heels of the company’s announced acquisition of Accession, which is expected to close by mid-Q3 2025. The firm raised its earnings estimates in […]
